response.overview: Raptor Island: A team of terrorist-fighting Naval officers in the South China Sea finds their struggle against the enemy taking a backseat to the fight of their lives when an horde of creatures thought to be extinct for millions of years descend upon them in an action-packed tale of man-versus-monster starring Steven Bauer and Lorenzo Lamas. Planet Raptor: In 2066, the planet is entirely occupied by raptors. The only hope for the human race is a group of marines. These are cheap movies with bad acting.
response.title: Planet Raptor Collection
